  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb2\u0bbe\u0baa\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba9\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0baf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Appeal if Lap Gas is sold at a higher price",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "It has been reported that the lab is making more profit by selling at a higher price than the retail price set for cooking gas.",
        "Therefore, the company has announced to inform immediately about those who sell at a higher price than the fixed price.",
        "Incidents have been reported in which lab gas cylinders were sold at a price higher than the retail price set for lab cooking gas, and ill-gotten gains were exerted to put pressure on consumers.",
        "If there are any complaints regarding LPG being sold at a higher price than the fixed price, please inform the consumer service department of the company at the speedy number 1345. The retail price of 12.5 lp LPG is Rs 6850.",
        "As well as the unavailability of cooking gas people are constantly waiting in many areas. So in order to make cooking gas available to consumers faster, we are further expanding the LOP distribution of cooking gas."
      ],
